#stance=stance1
#originalStanceText=Yes
#originalTopic=should-the-us-have-universal-healthcare
Whatever the system   health   will be rationed. With free enterprise   medicine   it will be rationed by the market; when you have a national health system you will have rationing of a somewhat different kind.  Rationing is inevitable; the only question to decide is how the rationing is to be done. America has chosen one path; other advanced countries have chosen another. 